name: Queen of Clubs
description: Bringing together various passions and aesthetic and emotional inspirations I arrived at a new personal project. Deck (so much the normal that besides I love it has an affective bond until the Tarot that I've always been enchanted in the figures, I'll represent three arcana of each suit), elements of nature (fire, air, earth and water) and tribes (piro in staying inventing attributing characteristics of a possible geographic location, customs, clothing, skin color, etc etc). And enfans, here is the first representation of the very powerful Queen of Clubs (the suit of clubs is linked to the fire element, the starting point for evolution, growth, the spirit) 🔥 I hope you enjoy it!
